(17, '2016-08-10 18:31:23', '2016-08-10 18:31:23', 'Leverate', 15, '', 'http://www.leverate.com', '200', 'Started in 2008 by a core team of software development experts, Leverate is the leading technology solutions provider in the Forex industry. The company focuses on developing innovative products meant to simplify running a Forex business, and takes client support to the next level, with dedicated account managers and customer support available 24 hours a day.\r\n\r\n Leverate has perfected the concept of a “brokerage in a box” with the release of LXSuite, containing all of the platforms and software needed to successfully manage a Forex brokerage, including an award-winning social trading platform, a robust risk management platform, the most accurate price feed on the market, a CRM platform created exclusively for brokers, all linked to a diverse and regulated liquidity pool of top tier suppliers.\r\n\r\n At the heart of the LXSuite solutions package lies Sirix, our flagship HTML5 social trading platform. Sirix features an intuitive user interface designed to make trading easy, and is built to shine in multiple trading environments. The platform is fully branded and comes with several advanced charting and analytics tools. Brokers running Sirix can give clients access to a huge social trading community, conceived to encourage and educate traders.', '', 'Dereh Sheshet Haymim 30 Bnei Brak', '', '', '', '', '1', 2, 0, 'Financial Services', 'Privately Held', '2008'),
