(46, '2016-08-23 16:34:40', '2016-08-23 16:36:22', 'NiNiSpeech', 22, '', 'http://www.ninispeech.com/', '50', 'NiNiSpeech enables people who stutter to take control of their speech in day to day life, using unique mobile feedback technologies. 1% of the population stutter, facing personal, social and professional challenges. Most people who stutter do well in the clinic, but outside in the real world, 84% lapse right back into their stuttering.\r\n \r\nResearch shows 84% of people who stutter will lapse back after treatment. NiNiSpeech helps beating these statistics. NiNiSpeech helps people who stutter achieve their speech goals, whether eloquence, confidence, acceptance or fluency. NiNiSpeech incorporates unique patented technologies, based on scientific grounds of treatment.\r\n\r\nNiNiSpeech offers people who stutter a safe platform to engage in speech activities, build confidence and experience spontaneous interaction with speech partners who share ambition, sensitivity and mutual commitment to make progress.\r\n \r\nSpeech Language Pathologists (SLP) can, for the very first time, gain insight into the clients\' speech in day-to-day life. Speech fluency metrics are generated automatically and objectively. The SLP views the clients\' speech performance using a browser dashboard, and even listen to recordings of stutter clusters', '', 'NiNiSpeech LTD.\r\n8a Hantke St., Haifa\r\nIsrael', '', '', '', 'info@ninispeech.com', '1', 5, 0, 'Health, Wellness and Fitness', 'Privately Held', '2014'),
