(49, '2016-08-25 19:19:24', '2016-08-25 19:19:28', 'Startica', 34, '', 'http://www.startica.co.il', '200', 'Startica is is a software provider to its customers comprehensive solutions in the field of software development and infrastructure. The company specializes in finding and placement of high quality personnel in a variety of high-tech positions. ', 'חברת סטרטיקה הינה בית תוכנה המספק ללקוחותיה פתרונות כוללים בתחום הפיתוח ותשתיות תוכנה.\r\nהחברה מתמחה באיתור והשמת כוח אדם איכותי במגוון מקצועות ההי-טק הן במיקור חוץ והן בהשמה. בחברה צוות מומחי משאבי אנוש בעל ניסיון רב שנים המתמחה באיתור (הד-האנטיג) ואבחון מועמדים הן בפן האישיותי והן בפן המקצועי. \r\nאנו מלווים את הלקוח משלב קבלת המשרה, איתור המועמד המתאים, אבחון אישיותי מעמיק, בחינה מקצועית מותאמת לסביבה הטכנולוגית והעסקית של הלקוח, ליווי ותאום הראיונות, בדיקת ממליצים,  והחתמת המועמד בהתאם לתקציב. אנו מקפידים על ליווי ושימור העובד ברמת שביעות רצון גבוה במהלך כל תקופת העסקתו.\r\nקבוצת מיקור החוץ בחברה מנוהלת על ידי צוות מומחים טכנולוגיים בכירים המלווים את לקוחות החברה ועובדיה ומעניקים תמיכה טכנולוגית המבוססת על ידע וניסיון מצטבר.\r\nלחברה מומחים במקצועות השונים כגון: מנתחי מערכות, מנהלי פרויקטים, ארכיטקטים, אנשי בדיקות, מומחים מתחום ההסבה ועוד.\r\nתחום פרוייקטים בחברה מנוהל על ידי מקצוענים בעולם התוכנה, חומרה ותשתיות המלווים את ביצוע הפרויקט משלב הייזום ועד עלייתו לאויר.\r\nתחום שיווק מוצרים – חברת סטרטיקה מתמחה בשיווק פתרונות לעולם השו"ב.', '27 Habarzel st. Orr Towers, Entrance A, Ramat Hachayal Tel Aviv 69710, Israel Tel-Aviv, Israel', '', '03-6544555', '03-6547555', '', '1', 4, 0, 'Human Resources', 'Privately Held', '2013'),
(50, '2016-08-29 11:01:10', '2016-08-29 11:01:14', 'Cynet', 70, '', 'http://www.cynet.com', '50', 'Cynet brings vast experience in automated persistent threat detection (APT), unmasking high risk vulnerabilities and shortcomings in the security landscape. Cynet provides a comprehensive agent-less solution for advanced threat detection and remediation.Taking a 360 degree view of the organization\'s networks, servers, files and users, Cynet enables real time monitoring, detection and remediation of malware and other threats. \r\n\r\nOur agent-less solution significantly reduces the time and cost of implementation and maintenance. We automatically collect and filter hundreds of indicators and run them through our multistage static and dynamic threat analysis. \r\n\r\nThe resulting alerts are classified and further examined by our market leading cyber security experts who provide the final eyes on glass analysis in cases where the security automation process yielded inconclusive results or unknown anomalies. Visit us today for more information at www.cynet.com.', '', '11 Moshe Levi Street (UMI Building)\r\n Rishon LeZion, Israel\r\n75070, Israel', '', '', '', 'info@cynet.com', '1', 4, 0, 'Computer & Network Security', 'Privately Held', '2014'),
(51, '2016-08-29 11:10:59', '2016-08-29 11:11:03', 'Veribo', 34, '', 'http://www.veribo.com', '50', 'Veribo is a premium online reputation management (ORM) company with headquarters in Tel Aviv. Established in 2007, Veribo serves large corporations and high profile individuals worldwide. Through tailor-made work strategies, we give our clients control over how they appear online. \r\n\r\nBuilding a professional or corporate reputation takes years of work, and a single media crisis can ruin it. Search results displaying unwanted or misleading press can directly affect the viability and profitability of your business and be personally damaging.\r\n\r\nOnline reputation management is the art of controlling the search results for your name on Google in order to build a positive online presence.  By creating and promoting relevant and quality content, Veribo suppresses unwanted results and lets you decide what people see when your name is googled.\r\n\r\nWith a controlled online presence, your key search results will present you like you deserve to be presented.\r\n\r\nA tailor-made image	\r\n\r\nWe develop a tailor-made strategy for each client in which we decide which online assets will work best to create the desired online image.\r\n\r\nUnwanted or negative search results cannot simply be removed from the search engines. ORM pushes down unwanted results to later pages of the search results where there is less chance that someone will read them. This is done by building new websites with positive, relevant content and promoting them to the first search results along with other positive articles already online.\r\n\r\nORM can be divided into two parallels courses: 1. promoting sites that are already online (official website and positive media articles) and 2. building new, high-quality websites that will be promoted to rank highly in the search engines. \r\n\r\nStrict confidentiality\r\n\r\nWe value the trust our clients give us and take extreme measures to keep information safe.', '', '2 Ibn Gabirol Street Tel-Aviv, Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 2, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2007'),
(52, '2016-08-29 11:21:41', '2016-08-29 11:21:44', 'Feedvisor', 34, '', 'http://www.feedvisor.com', '200', 'Feedvisor is the pioneer of Algo-Commerce – the discipline of using Big Data and Machine Learning Algorithms to make business-critical decisions for online retailers.\r\n\r\nFeedvisor’s cloud-based Algorithmic Repricing and Revenue Intelligence solutions power millions of pricing decisions daily; providing retailers with actionable insights to maximize profitability and drive their business growth.\r\n\r\nFeedvisor was founded in 2011 and has since become a true market leader. In the last year alone, Feedvisor’s customer base has grown by 250% and over $1billion in GMV is managed on the Feedvisor platform. Clients have seen results of up to 500% increase in sales and 40% increase in profit margins.\r\n\r\nFeedvisor’s technology has won several prestigious industry awards, including the Red Herring Top 100 Global in 2014, and Frost and Sullivan’s Technology Leadership Award 2014.\r\nVisit us at www.feedvisor.com.', '', 'Igal Alon 126 Tel Aviv, Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 2, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2011');
