(53, '2016-08-29 11:30:37', '2016-08-29 11:30:42', 'Firstimpression', 34, '', 'http://www.firstimpression.io', '50', 'FirstImpression analyzes the unique layout of every webpage and its corresponding user behavior to create the perfect ad placement for every page view. With no coding involved and featuring over fifteen dynamic ad products, FirstImpression maximizes revenue for every website and spikes user engagement.    \r\n\r\nOur platform overcomes the hardships brought with hard-coded ad placements. In today’s multi-screen/platform/device environment tailoring the right placement for every page layout is critical for ensuring a good user experience and high engagement. With FirstImpression, every time a webpage loads, an X-ray is taken and sent to our server for analysis. The server then determines if a legitimate opportunity to show an ad placement has been presented and, if so, how to best construct the placement, in what format, and how to position it.\r\n\r\nFirstImpression offers an easy, flexible, and super quick solution to create any type of ad placement in seconds - a technological solution that brings a tailored advertising experience at scale. \r\n', '', '7 Dubnov Street, Tel Aviv, Israel, 6473207', '', '+972 (3) 374-1235', '+972 (3) 374-1283', 'info@firstimpression.io', '1', 2, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2013'),
