(60, '2016-08-30 19:06:52', '2016-08-30 19:06:55', 'Dorbel', 34, '', 'https://www.dorbel.com', '10', 'We are on a mission to digitize the entire process of renting and leasing an apartment (as it ought to be in 2016). There are many exciting features we are incorporating - from a virtual tour inside the apartment to automatic transfer of utility bills after renting (e.g. Electricity, gas, etc.) and much more!', '', '129 Rothschild Boulevard Tel Aviv, Israel Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 5, 0, 'Internet', 'Self Owned', '2015'),
(61, '2016-08-31 19:06:07', '2016-08-31 19:06:11', 'SentinelOne', 15, '', 'http://www.sentinelone.com', '200', 'SentinelOne is changing the economics of cyber attacks through a unique, platform-based approach that combines next-generation endpoint protection with innovative endpoint detection and response features that ensure advanced, targeted attacks are not only detected but also prevented.  At the core of SentinelOne’s Endpoint Protection Platform (EPP) is a lightweight module that continuously analyzes suspicious behavioral patterns across Windows, OS X, and Android based systems.  As patterns are identified as malicious, the EPP launches a series of automated responses to quickly mitigate the threat, immunize other endpoints, and remediate systems to their pre-attack state.\r\n\r\nSentinelOne is the first and only next-generation endpoint protection solution that has been certified by AV-TEST, the Independent IT-Security Institute.  If you’d like to learn how organizations big and small are replacing legacy antivirus solutions with next-generation endpoint protection please follow us on LinkedIn and Twitter, or visit our website at www.sentinelone.com.', '', '21 Bar Kochva St\r\nBnei Brak , 5126001', '', '+972-775215506', '', '', '1', 9, 0, 'Computer & Network Security', 'Privately Held', '2013'),
(62, '2016-08-31 20:09:15', '2016-08-31 20:09:19', 'SuperCom', 23, '', 'http://www.supercom.com', '200', 'Since 1988, SuperCom(NASDAQ:SPCB) has been a leading global provider of traditional and digital identity solutions, providing advanced safety, identification and security solutions to governments and organizations, both private and public, throughout the world. Through its proprietary e-Government platforms and innovative solutions for traditional and biometrics enrollment, personalization, issuance and border control services, SuperCom has inspired governments and national agencies to design and issue secured Multi-ID documents and robust digital identity solutions to its citizens and visitors. \r\n\r\nSuperCom offers advanced, secure mobile payments ranging from mobile wallet to mobile POS, using a set of components and platforms to enable secure mobile payments and financial services. SuperCom is a global provider of a unique all-in-one field-proven RFID & mobile PureSecurity advanced solutions suite, accompanied by advanced complementary services for various industries, including healthcare and homecare, security and safety, community public safety, law enforcement, electronic monitoring, livestock monitoring, and building and access automation.', '', '1 Arie Shenkar Street, Herzliya 4672501, Israel', '', '+972.9.889.0880', '+972.9.889.0814', 'general@supercom.com', '1', 5, 0, 'Information Technology and Services', 'Public Company', '1988'),
(63, '2016-08-31 20:53:31', '2016-08-31 20:54:26', 'Personali', 34, '', 'http://www.personali.com', '50', 'Personali™ enables consumers to personalize their own eCommerce incentives in real-time, driving dramatic increases in average unit retail (AUR) and incremental revenue for retailers. Our technology applies principles of behavioral economics and consumer psychology to trigger emotionally-driven buying experiences, increasing loyalty by as much as 65% and sales by an average of 32%.\r\n\r\nWe partner with some of the largest retailers in the USA, Latin America and Europe. \r\nPersonali\'s meaningful experiences have generated over $400M USD for our clients.\r\n\r\nInternet, Retail, eCommerce, Travel, Behavioral Economics, Telecommunications, Consumer Psychology', '', 'Tel-Aviv', '', '972 3 744 2011', '', '', '1', 6, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2011'),
(64, '2016-08-31 21:03:59', '2016-08-31 21:04:08', 'AppsFlyer', 23, '', 'http://www.appsflyer.com', '200', 'AppsFlyer is the leading mobile advertising attribution and marketing analytics platform, enabling app marketers, brands and ad agencies to measure their marketing campaigns across more than 1,900 integrated media partners. As a Facebook Mobile Measurement Partner, Google Official Partner, and Twitter Official Partner, AppsFlyer provides mobile advertisers with unbiased attribution, mobile campaign analytics, in-app user engagement tracking, lifetime value analysis, ROI and retargeting attribution.\r\n\r\nOur real-time dashboard, NativeTrackTM and OneLink smart deeplinking, provide advertisers the tools they need to achieve the optimal return on their marketing dollars. AppsFlyer currently serves more than 10,000 advertisers, measures more than $4 billion in annual mobile ad spend and tracks more than 1 billion installs and 200 billion mobile actions every month. Noteworthy clients include Playtika, IHG, Alibaba, Baidu, Trivago, Macy’s, Samsung, DeNA, and HBO. \r\n\r\nMobile Apps Marketing, Marketing, iPhone, Android, App Store, iOS, Google Play, Advertising, Mobile Measurement, Attribution Analytics, Deep Linking', '', '85 Medinat Hayehudim St Herzliya, 4676672 Israel', '', '+972-9-768-1949', '', 'contact@appsflyer.com', '1', 4, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2011'),
(65, '2016-08-31 21:20:25', '2016-08-31 21:20:35', 'Travolutionary', 34, '', 'http://www.travolutionary.com', '10', 'Travolutionary empowers some of the world\'s leading travel brands to stay competitive in the cut-throat online consolidation travel space. The rise of metasearch and the convergence of accommodation e-commerce is putting smaller and medium sized online players at a disadvantage, making it virtually impossible to compete with market leaders when sourcing travel products for sale online. \r\n\r\nWith our leading edge technology and \'Travolutionary\' approach to problem solving, we can not only help you compete effectively, but also manage your pricing efficiently, improve conversions and maximise profits. \r\n\r\nOur proprietary technology platform now provides access to all major OTA direct and negotiated rates as well as over 70 wholesale bed banks, totalling close to 1 Million unique accommodation options available online for instant reservation. We have taken out all the hassle of aggregating and geo-tagging properties so you can focus on what you do best - selling. \r\n\r\nWe are a driven, solutions focused team with a wealth of technology and travel experience that understands the pain points you face and knows what you need to stay ahead of the game. Visit our website at http://www.travolutionary.com for a demo or contact our team to arrange a consultation and audit of your product. We can show you exactly how we will save you money, improve your inventory, create a more satisfying experience for your customer and, most importantly, increase your profits. ', '', '59 Hamasger, Tel Aviv, Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 8, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2010'),
(66, '2016-08-31 22:48:14', '2016-08-31 22:48:18', 'Wochit', 34, '', 'https://www.wochit.com', '200', 'Wochit is a video creation platform empowering newsrooms, creators and brands to capture and expand audience attention through the power of video. Founded in 2012, Wochit makes video accessible for anyone to produce and share at scale across all social and digital platforms. With Wochit, videos can be created quickly, using pre-negotiated, rights-cleared assets from AP, Reuters, Getty, Bloomberg and many more sources. Wochit is the winner of both the Gutenberg Prize for its disruptive technology in the field of journalism and Digiday’s Best Video Technology Innovation for its positive impact on clients’ bottom line.\r\n\r\nAs video consumption and share of overall online audience continues to multiply, organizations of all sizes are under increasing pressure to make video a standard to all owned content practices. Wochit makes this possible in one efficient platform, and does so on behalf of media brands worldwide including Gannett, AOL, The Week, Die Welt, Der Spiegel, ProSieben, YLE Kioski, NRC Media and La Repubblica. The Company is backed by Cedar Fund, Greycroft Partners, Marker LLC and Redpoint Ventures. Wochit is based in New York, with offices in London and Tel Aviv.', '', '5 Sderot Menachem Begin, POB 3\r\nBeit Dagan 5025001\r\nIsrael', '', '+972 3 6203699', '', '', '1', 5, 0, 'Computer Software', 'Privately Held', '2012'),
(67, '2016-09-05 09:51:36', '2016-09-05 09:51:41', 'Proacts', 34, '', 'http://www.proacts.com', '50', 'Proacts bridges the gap between collaboration and communication ensuring safe communities around the world. We emphasize the importance of playing a role in your own safety: utilize humans as sensors to send updates and concerns via audio, video and text message to anticipate and prevent crime, terror and natural disasters. Couple this real-time information with open-faced sources and trends on social media, in a back-and-forth style of communication with our expert desk to dispatch the necessary help.  We adapt alongside the changing technological mannerisms and advancements, and put the mechanism in place for your safety, 24/7.\r\n\r\nmobile, anticipation, human sensors, geolocation, picture message, safe cities, crisis management, emergency response, command and control, communication, crowd wisdom, civilian protection, technology first, need-to-know basis, users as sensors, real-time', '', 'Levinstein Tower,\r\n23 Menahem Begin Street,\r\nTel Aviv, Israel', '', '+972-3-9473030', '+972-3-9473020', 'contact@proacts.com', '1', 2, 0, 'Public Safety', 'Privately Held', '2012'),
(68, '2016-09-05 10:00:23', '2016-09-05 10:00:38', 'Aman Group', 15, '', 'http://aman.co.il', '5000', 'Aman group is a leading Information Technology solutions supplier in Israel also active internationally, providing state of the art IT products and services.\r\n\r\nAman Group specializes in providing specific advanced services & products in the fields of data integration, virtualization and networking, Information & cyber security, command and control, software development, knowledge management, UX&design, Output management verification and more.\r\n\r\nAman Group represents a wide range of advanced solutions, each a leader in its own field, some of them exclusively represented. \r\nAmong them:\r\nInformatica, Palo Alto Networks, Citrix, Kaspersky, Airtight, Cyberark, HP and more. \r\n\r\nBased on our successful activity and partnership, Aman was chosen by its partners to become a distributor in East Europe. \r\n\r\nAman Group also provides a wide range of outsourcing services in several models – some of them are unique in the Israeli market - from overall responsibility over organizational IT systems, Data Centers, operation and maintenance of organizational communication networks, comprehensive Help Desk services, systems\' infrastructure management, management of data protection and communications infrastructures, to Near-shore and off -shore solutions and providing experts in specific fields according to the organization\'s targeted needs.\r\n\r\nAmong our customers are most of the leading Israeli companies in the industry banking and finances, health, telecom, Security &defense, government /public sectors, Hi-tech and more.\r\n\r\nCitrix, Informatica, Trillium, Finance, Security Information, infrastructure, AS-400, Development, CRM, Digital Distribution, Outsourcing', '', 'Baruh Hirsh 28\r\nBnei Brak, 51202', '', '03-6173737', '073-2016920', 'info@aman.co.il', '1', 2, 0, 'Computer Software', 'Privately Held', '1974'),
(69, '2016-09-05 10:23:13', '2016-09-05 10:23:18', 'Vidazoo', 34, '', 'http://vidazoo.com', '', 'Vidazoo is an all in one yield management platform for video. Our mission is to lead and inspire the advertising industry by building the most clever technology. We are a bunch of tech and business experts who created one of the most powerful platforms for video streaming and serving. \r\n\r\nWe specialize in developing high end products for publishers with a focus on programmatic video monetization across Display, Mobile and Connected TV. Our holistic solution and fine tuning to small details is what makes our clients perform better in all aspects.', '', 'Dubnov St 7, \r\nTel Aviv-Yafo, Israel', '', '', '', 'info@vidazoo.com', '1', 2, 0, 'Marketing and Advertising', 'Privately Held', '2014'),
(70, '2016-09-05 10:50:57', '2016-09-05 10:51:00', 'Bitshakers', 23, '', 'http://bitshakers.com', '50', 'BitShakers is a boutique technology house, specialising in desktop and browser applications with special focus on games, video and e-commerce solutions.\r\n\r\nBitShakers is home to a variety of products that provide an engaging and productive online experience for your users.\r\n\r\nWe build, market and deliver a wide variety of social and entertainment products, all conceptualized and developed in-house and some in cooperation with our partners.\r\n\r\nBased on years of experience in developing and monetizing browser add-ons; we have successfully distributed our services to millions of users worldwide.\r\n\r\nAs a desktop app and browser add-on developer, BitShakers boasts a rapidly expanding user base. Our strong, existing product line and high technological, in-house capabilities as well as our very own distribution channels, are all key factors directly contributing to our clients’ success.\r\n\r\nDesktop Applications, Browser Extensions, Monetization, Development, Distribution', '', 'HaNadiv St 71 \r\nHerzliyyaa, Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 0, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2011'),
(71, '2016-09-05 11:37:28', '2016-09-05 11:37:32', 'Shoppimon', 34, '', 'http://www.shoppimon.com', '10', 'Shoppimon is a comprehensive free monitoring solution for Magento shops that keeps an eye on your store...so you don\'t have to. When your Magento store has a technical glitch (and it does happen), customers leave. Shoppimon robots – aka Shoppimonsters – alert you to problems so you can keep customers on your site until the sale is closed.\r\n\r\nIt’s a ridiculously simple tool, with no scripting and no changes to Magento necessary. In just a few minutes, Shoppimonsters identify the most important user scenarios on your site and determine whether or not they are working correctly.\r\n\r\nOur suite of diagnostic tools can help you boost sales by improving your customer experience. Shoppimonsters check out your store’s functionality, and then you receive a detailed report showing you exactly where the issues are so you can fix them. Errors detected can include: server, application, SSL, JavaScript and widget errors, missing pages, missing elements (e.g. images), broken links, and a whole lot more. Let us help you get the most out of your Magento store.\r\n\r\nmagento, Performance monitoring', '', '3 Levontin St. Tel Aviv, Israel', '', '', '', 'info@shoppimon.com', '1', 1, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2014'),
(72, '2016-09-05 11:56:02', '2016-09-05 11:56:05', 'K Logic', 34, '', 'http://k.co.il', '200', 'K Logic (www.k.co.il) is one of Israel’s leading Online Marketing companies, serving Fortune 1000’s as well as start-ups worldwide in sectors such as Communications, Publishing, Banking, Insurance and Technology. K Logic serves as a strategic partner to its clients through its commitment to delivering results on a firm basis of creativity, technology and incredibly great thinking.\r\n\r\nDigital Transformation, Costumer journey architecture, Thought leadership, Data science, Online Marketing, Content strategy, User acquisition (SEM, SEO, ASO, Inbound, Media performance), Marketing technology integration', '', 'Temkin 16, Tel-Aviv', '', '03-6253333', '03-6253330', '', '1', 4, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2006'),
(73, '2016-09-05 12:25:39', '2016-09-05 12:25:42', 'Seperia', 23, '', 'http://www.seperia.com', '50', 'Seperia delivers performance driven digital marketing services to boost clients’ digital marketing results, building and optimizing their marketing programs for scale and efficiency. Our services include search, display, social, analytics and conversion optimization. \r\n\r\nSeperia’s digital marketing services and technology are employed by companies operating in some of the most competitive global online markets, in over 80 countries and 50 languages.\r\n\r\nWe developed the Edge.BI SaaS platform to empower managers and optimizers to operate efficiently within data-intensive spaces and achieve the best results possible.\r\n\r\nAs a digital marketing pioneer in Israel, we established Seperia College to share the knowledge and experience gained in-house, train new generations of on-line marketing professionals and develop our own team.\r\n\r\nPPC Management, SEO, Mobile Marketing, Web Analytics, Edge.BI software, PPC course @ Seperia College', '', '6 Galgaley Haplada St. Herzelia Pituach, Israel', '', '+972-9-9509286', '', 'info@seperia.com', '1', 2, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2003'),
(74, '2016-09-05 15:49:33', '2016-09-05 15:52:07', 'DiACardio', 11, '', 'http://www.diacardio.com', '50', 'DiACardio LTD is a revolutionary decision support tools company for cardiologist using echocardiography.\r\nDiACardio\'s proprietary technology is a unique and innovative platform, capable of automatic detection the left ventricular (LV) wall borders and adds to the echo evaluation the ability to assess quantitatively the dynamic performance of the heart.', '', 'Haenergia st\' 77 Gev-Yam Industrial Park Beer-Sheva, Israel', '', '+972-777648318', '+972-777648318', 'info@diacardio.com', '1', 3, 0, 'Medical Devices', 'Privately Held', '2009'),
(75, '2016-09-05 16:34:39', '2016-09-05 16:34:43', 'Keywee', 34, '', 'http://www.keywee.co', '50', 'Keywee offers publishers and marketers a new approach to content distribution and performance measurement. Its revolutionary platform employs advanced text-mining technology and a vast database of historical content performance to help publishers, retailers, and brands find the audiences most likely to meet specific business goals for their content. Keywee’s customers include The British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC), Conde Nast, National Geographic, The New York Times and Slate. Backed by leading investors including Eric Schmidt’s Innovation Endeavors and Marker LLC, as well as The New York Times Company, the company is headquartered in New York and Tel Aviv.', '', 'Rehov Harav Kook 17 \r\n6330256 Tel Aviv-Yafo \r\nIsrael', '', '', '', '', '1', 4, 0, 'Computer Software', 'Privately Held', '2013'),
(76, '2016-09-06 10:13:30', '2016-09-06 10:13:36', 'Drippler', 34, '', 'http://drippler.com', '50', 'Drippler helps consumers make the most of their technology. We\'re disrupting the consumer tech-support industry by leveraging community and AI to provide a frictionless, remote experience.\r\n\r\nLooking for high LTV users for your mobile app? Drippler connects your app with our millions of users. The result for your app is installs that deliver. Learn more here: http://drippler.com/advertisers\r\n\r\nDrippler on Google Play:  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.drippler.android.updates\r\nDrippler on the App Store:  https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/drippler-updates-tips-apps/id619307903?mt=8\r\n\r\nTech Support, Mobile User Acquisition, Mobile Advertising, Mobile Apps', '', 'Yosef Karo 19, Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel', '', '', '', '', '1', 1, 0, 'Internet', 'Privately Held', '2010');
