(75, '2016-08-20 23:40:12', '2016-08-20 23:44:24', 0, 'BI Analyst', '', 37, 'What you need: \r\n• Analyze the different data sources, create and measure KPIs to reach actionable recommendations for business decisions\r\n•Work with management, marketing, research and development, and business teams to provide them with insights\r\n•Develop data-based models and tools for product monitoring and user targeting\r\n•Create forecasts and simulations to improve product performance\r\n•Be the owner of the data, design and lead the data structure of our products\r\nWhat you need:\r\n•B.A/BSc degree in areas of industrial engineering or data science\r\n•Strong analytical skills required\r\n•SQL knowledge must\r\n•Passionate for data, curious to learn and improve\r\n•Fast learner, strong technical comprehension, ability to multitask', '', 49, 0, 'Full-time', 9, 401, 9, 400, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '1', '', ''),
